      "span_text": "Referring to the research of the study that examined the sea surface height differences between the western Pacific Ocean and the eastern Indian Ocean  , this study aims to examine the differences in SST of both those oceans at the time of ENSO. The category of SST which to be studied in this research are the variability and the difference of SST in north and south of Indonesia."
